        <h1>Overview</h1>
        <p>A combination of the words "anime" and "figures". We specialise in selling figures of your beloved characters for your collection! Don't let our name fool you; we also have figures of video game characters and other Japanese media. 
        We are a Brunei-based shop and we get our goods directly from Japan!</p>
    
        <h2>History</h2>
        <p>Anifigures was founded in 2015, and was formed to bring happiness and the thrill of figure-collecting to our fellow otakus in Brunei! We have our branch located at Batu Satu, and we have been serving customers since then.</p>
    
        <h2>Our Goal</h2>
        <p>We are dedicated to bringing customers original and quality goods at a reasonable price. We are completely against counterfeits and bootlegs, so you will not be seeing that nonesense here.</p>
